    <link href="https://dongmingtech.com/2019/07/03/rpi-crazyflie-kubeedge-example/"/>
    <id>https://dongmingtech.com/2019/07/03/rpi-crazyflie-kubeedge-example/</id>
    <published>2019-07-02T18:18:11.000Z</published>
    <updated>2019-07-02T18:29:26.480Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>基于kubeedge并通过树莓派3控制四轴飞行器crazyflie2.0悬停</p><p>构建树莓派镜像并配置crazyflie运行环境</p><p>在树莓派上构建镜像, 可以选取ubuntu:latest镜像,或者debian:jessie镜像<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">docker pull ubuntu:latest</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>更新ubuntu国内源，可参考博客:<a href="https://cfreebuf.github.io/2019/06/28/ubuntu-18-04-%E4%BF%AE%E6%94%B9%E4%B8%BA%E5%9B%BD%E5%86%85%E6%BA%90/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">如何更新ubuntu18.04 aliyun源</a></p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">apt-get install python3 python3-pip libusb-dev</span><br><span class="line">pip3 install pyusb&gt;=1.0.0b2 libusb1</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>提交容器修改内容并生成本地镜像, 可参考文章：<a href="https://cfreebuf.github.io/2019/06/28/%E5%9F%BA%E4%BA%8E%E5%B7%B2%E6%9C%89%E9%95%9C%E5%83%8F%E5%88%B6%E4%BD%9C%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E7%9A%84Docker%E9%95%9C%E5%83%8F/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">如何修改容器并生成镜像</a></p><p>详细代码请参考<a href="https://github.com/cfreebuf/kubeedge-examples" target="_blank" rel="noopener">此例子github地址</a></p>]]></content>
    
    <summary type="html">
    
      
      
