    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>树莓派连接公司wifi时，wifi名称显示为灰色不可连接。<br>如图所示：</p><h2 id><a href="#" class="headerlink" title></a><img src="/2019/06/24/树莓派连接WPA2-Wifi/invalid-wifi.jpg" alt></h2><p>解决方案：<br>修改wifi配置文件:</p><h2 id="vim-etc-wpa-supplicant-wpa-supplicant-conf"><a href="#vim-etc-wpa-supplicant-wpa-supplicant-conf" class="headerlink" title="vim /etc/wpa_supplicant/wpa_supplicant.conf"></a><code>vim /etc/wpa_supplicant/wpa_supplicant.conf</code></h2><p>新增配置：<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">network=&#123;</span><br><span class="line">ssid=&quot;your_AP_name&quot;</span><br><span class="line">  scan_ssid=1</span><br><span class="line">key_mgmt=WPA-EAP</span><br><span class="line">eap=PEAP</span><br><span class="line">identity=&quot;your username&quot;</span><br><span class="line">password=&quot;your password&quot;</span><br><span class="line">phase1=&quot;peapver=0&quot;</span><br><span class="line">phase2=&quot;MSCHAPV2&quot;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><hr><p>参考链接：<br><a href="https://rollingstarky.github.io/2018/10/16/raspberry-pi-wifi-wpa2-eap/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://rollingstarky.github.io/2018/10/16/raspberry-pi-wifi-wpa2-eap/</a><br><a href="https://blog.csdn.net/qq_22716879/article/details/51416322" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://blog.csdn.net/qq_22716879/article/details/51416322</a></p>]]></content>
    
